{"type": "article", "id": 7700, "title": "Paul Smith 定制 Defender", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-24T08:46:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234530fqY2pgk5yIMXRj16.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tLand Rover 此前宣布将会在其 70 周年之际推出全新的 Defender 车系，最近他们联手英国时尚品牌 Paul Smith 送 Defender “最后一程”，推出了一款定制版 Defender，Paul Smith 手下的车身外观具备其将他调色盘式的设计风格，选取了 27 种不同配色，且融入Smith 经典的彩条元素。更有趣的是车顶的一只手绘大黄蜂，看上去动感又幽默。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234526ZRBV41Gw8aWyYduM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234526ViC3ns6Pr2Y17ANX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234527yEDT5sC79PbBu43w.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234528UkTMipY2Z40bfaFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234528SLkcuERs2WaQ05Mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234529JGdHnzW1ZBFm5VEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66628702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}